videos.headline: Tua hits Ruggs for quick 45-yard TD
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa finds Henry Ruggs III on a short pass and he takes it 45 yards to the house on Alabama's first drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua hits Ruggs for quick 45-yard TD) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua airmails 74-yard TD pass to Ruggs
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa sends a long pass to Henry Ruggs III for a 74 yard score, the duo's second touchdown connection of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua airmails 74-yard TD pass to Ruggs) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua tallies 3rd TD pass of the 1st half
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws to a wide open Najee Harris for a five-yard touchdown vs. Southern Mississippi.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua tallies 3rd TD pass of the 1st half) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua finds Jeudy uncovered for 4th TD pass
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa delivers his fourth touchdown pass of the first half, this time to Jerry Jeudy from 17 yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua finds Jeudy uncovered for 4th TD pass) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alabama DB makes over-the-shoulder INT
videos.description: Jack Abraham's pass attempt is intercepted by Alabama's Trevon Diggs in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alabama DB makes over-the-shoulder INT) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua, Jeudy team up for 2nd TD connection
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa throws his fifth touchdown pass and Jerry Jeudy catches his second vs. Southern Mississippi.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tua, Jeudy team up for 2nd TD connection) 2019/09/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tua throws 5 TDs for 2nd straight game
videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa tosses five touchdown passes to tie an Alabama school record in the Crimson Tide's 49-7 rout vs. Southern Mississippi.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Tua throws 5 TDs for 2nd straight game) 2019/09/21 ESHEET SOTFULL
